Peter Jones 'mai matukar fushi' bayan Holly Willoughby ta soke yarjejeniyar £11-miliyan
Dan wasan kwaikwayo na Peter Jones ya yi 'haushi' bayan mai gabatar da talabijin Holly Willoughby ya soke yarjejeniyar £11-million tare da kasuwancin kamfaninsa na rayuwa don mayar da hankali kan sabbin kwangilarta da Marks da Spencer da ITV
Willoughby ba ta da lokaci don kayan aikin gida da kayan haɗi, Truly.
An kwatanta kasuwancin ma'aurata da kamfanin Gwyneth Paltrow, Goop.
Mai gabatar da wannan safiyar, 37, ta bayyana a shafin Instagram don sanar da cewa za ta tafi.
Holly Willoughby ta sa dan wasan kwaikwayo na Peter Jones ya yi fushi sosai saboda ta soke kasancewa wani ɓangare na kasuwancin su na kamfanin lifestyle mai ban sha'awa na ƙarshe - don mayar da hankali kan manyan kwangilarta tare da Marks & Spencer da ITV.
Majiyoyin sun ce Jones ya "yi fushi sosai" lokacin da shahararren mashahurin talabijin din ya yarda a wani taro mai tsawo a ranar Talata a hedkwatar kasuwancinsa na Marlow, Buckinghamshire, cewa sabbin yarjejeniyoyinsa - da suka kai darajar £1.5m - sun bayyana cewa ba a bar isasshen lokaci don sadaukar da su ga kamfanin kayan gida da kayan haɗi, Truly.
An kwatanta kasuwancin da kamfanin Gwyneth Paltrow Goop kuma an yi imanin cewa zai ninka darajar Willoughby na £11-miliyan.
Da zarar Willoughby, 37, ta bayyana a Instagram don sanar da cewa za ta bar Truly, Jones ya bar Burtaniya kuma ya tafi ɗaya daga cikin ƙauyukansa.
Wata majiya ta ce: "Truly ita ce ta fi muhimmanci ga Holly.
Zai zama nata dogon lokaci nan gaba da zai cika 'yan shekarun da suka gabata.
Shawarta ta fita ta ba kowa mamaki.
Babu wanda ya gaskata abin da ke faruwa a ranar Talata, ƙaddamarwa ta kusan zuwa.
Akwai wani babban kantin sayar da kayayyaki a hedkwatar Marlow da ke shirye don sayarwa".
Masana sun yi imanin cewa barin mai gabatar da wannan safiyar, wanda ke cikin manyan masu samun riba a Burtaniya, na iya haifar da kashe miliyoyin miliyoyin ga kamfanin saboda babban saka hannun jari a cikin kayayyaki daga kyandirori da kyandirori zuwa tufafi da kayayyakin gida, da kuma yiwuwar ƙarin jinkiri har zuwa sake ƙaddamarwa.
Kuma hakan zai iya kawo ƙarshen abokantaka mai kyau.
Mahaifiyar yara uku, Willoughby da matarsa Rachel Dan Baldwin sun kasance abokai da Jones da matarsa Tara Capp na shekaru goma.
Willoughby ya kafa Truly tare da Capp a 2016 kuma Jones, 52, ya shiga tare da su a matsayin shugaban shugaban a watan Maris.
Ma'aurata suna tafiya tare kuma Jones yana da kashi 40 cikin dari a kamfanin samar da talabijin na Baldwin.
Willoughby za ta zama jakadan kamfanin M&S kuma za ta maye gurbin Ant McPartlin a matsayin mai gabatar da shirin ITV na I'm A Celebrity.
A daren jiya, wata majiya kusa da Jones ta ce "Ba mu da wata magana game da harkokin tattalin arzikinsa".
