Taron Trump a West Virginia, Tashar Youtube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara zanga-zangar yakin neman zabe da daddare a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shine farkon zanga-zangar Trump daga cikin biyar da aka tsara a mako mai zuwa, gami da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da aka dakatar da zaben tabbatar da zabensa don cike gurbin da ke gaban kotun kolin, Trump na son gina goyon baya a zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar wa'adin da ke tafe, yayin da 'yan Republican ke fuskantar barazanar rasa iko a majalisar dokoki a lokacin da aka kada kuri'un a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne zanga-zangar Trump a West Virginia a daren yau kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon ta ta yanar gizo?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia a karfe 7 na yamma ET yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon zanga-zangar Trump a West Virginia a kan layi a ƙasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Ana sa ran Trump zai yi jawabi a zaman da aka yi a wannan makon na neman zaben babban alkalin kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya yi tsanani saboda zargin cin zarafin jima'i da aka yi da kuri'ar amincewa da zaben majalisar dattijai da aka dakatar har tsawon mako guda yayin da FBI ke bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan zanga-zangar shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican su fuskanci zaben watan Nuwamba don samun ci gaba.
A cewar kamfanin yakin neman zaben na Shugaba Trump, zanga-zangar biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa na nufin "karfafa masu sa kai da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai", a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga wannan al'amari da shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama yayin da muke gab da shiga wani babban yakin neman zabe", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump wanda ya ki bayyana sunansa.
An shirya shi ne a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, zanga-zangar da daddare na iya tattara magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ta jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia a karo na biyu a cikin watan da ya gabata, jihar da ya lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin dari a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na West Virginia Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke shan kaye a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo don ya yi kokarin tura shi cikin binciken", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
