Turai ta yi gaba da 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar cin kofin Ryder
Turai za ta yi nasara a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup bayan da ta tashi daga wasannin hudu da hudu a ranar Asabar da ta ci Amurka da ci 10-6.
Ma'aurata masu ban sha'awa Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun yi ƙoƙari tare da cin nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods wanda ya sami wahalar ɗaukar ƙimar su gaba da Le Golf National zuwa maki huɗu.
Kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, da ke son rike kambun da ta rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta mamaye kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Amurka da ta yi kuskure a wasan hudu da safe, inda ta dauki wasan 3-1.
Amurka ta ba da ƙarin juriya a cikin foursomes, ta lashe wasanni biyu, amma ba za ta iya kaiwa ga bambancin ci ba.
Jim Furyk ya bukaci maki takwas daga wasanni 12 na ranar Lahadi don riƙe kyautar.
Fleetwood shine sabon Turai na farko a kakar wasa wanda ya ci kwallaye hudu a jere yayin da shi da Molinari, wanda aka yiwa lakabi da Molliwood bayan wasan karshen mako ne kawai su biyu da suka ci kwallaye hudu a wasanninsu na farko a tarihin Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun mamaye Woods da Patrick Reed a cikin hudu, sai suka yi aiki sosai don cinye Woods wanda ba shi da kyau da kuma sabon dan wasan Amurka na kakar wasa Bryson Dechambeau tare da karin fifiko na 5 & 4.
Woods, wanda ya sha wahala a wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna wasu lokuta na kwarewa amma yanzu ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasansa 29 a cikin hudu da hudu da bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, mai son wasan kwallon kafa na safe, ya dawo ga abokin aikinsa Henrik Stenson a cikin hudu don rasa 2&1 na Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka - waɗanda ke matsayi na farko da na uku a duniya.
Amma ba abin da Turai ta yi tsammani ya faru a ranar da ta yi kyau ba, da aka yi bikin aure a kudancin birnin Paris.
Jordan Spieth, babban zakara sau uku, da Justin Thomas sun kafa iyaka ga Amurkawa da maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun sami nasara mai ban tsoro na 2&1 akan Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter na Spain a cikin hudu kuma daga baya suka dawo don cin Poulter da Rory McIlroy da 4&3 a cikin hudu bayan sun rasa ramuka biyu na farko.
Sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin Ryder Cup da wata kungiya ta dawo daga tazarar maki hudu yayin da ta shiga cikin singles, kodayake masu rike da Furyk suna bukatar wani abu don riƙe kyautar.
Duk da haka, bayan da aka biyu-mafi kyau ga kwana biyu, Lahadi ta counterattack alama za su zama fiye da za su iya yi.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za ta taba yin watsi da makaman ba tare da amincewa ba
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa, takunkumin da ake ci gaba da sanyawa kasar na kara janyo rashin amincewarsu da Amurka kuma babu yadda kasar za ta yi ta yi watsi da makaman nukiliyarta a karkashin irin wannan yanayi.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa babban taron shekara-shekara na kungiyar duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki wasu matakai masu kyau a cikin shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da makaman nukiliya, lalata wurin gwajin nukiliya, da kuma yin alkawarin hana yaduwar makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya.
Duk da haka, ba mu ga amsa mai dacewa daga Amurka ba, in ji shi.
Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba, ba za a amince da tsaron kasa ba, kuma a irin wannan yanayi ba za mu taba yin watsi da kanmu ba. 
Yayin da Ri ya maimaita korafe-korafen da aka saba yi daga Koriya ta Arewa kan tsayayyar da Washington ke yi wa tsarin 'matakai-mataki' na yaduwar nukiliya wanda a ciki ake ba wa Koriya ta Arewa lada idan ta dauki matakai a hankali, sanarwar tasa ta nuna a fili cewa ba ta yi watsi da yaduwar nukiliya ba kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi nuni ne ga wata sanarwa ta hadin gwiwa da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka fitar a taron koli na farko da aka taba yi tsakanin shugaban Amurka mai ci da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni, inda Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki kan "yantar da kariya daga nukiliya a yankin Koriya" yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbatar da tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta nemi kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce Pyongyang dole ne ta fara ba da makaman nukiliyarta.
Washington ta kuma yi tsayayya da kira da a sassauta tsauraran takunkumin kasa da kasa kan Koriya ta Arewa.
Amurka ta dage kan denuclearization first da kara matsin lamba ta hanyar  takunkumi don cimma burinsu ta hanyar tilastawa, har ma da kin amincewa da  sanarwar kawo karshen yakin, in ji Ri.
Ganin cewa takunkumi zai iya karya mu mafarkin mutanen da basu san mu ba ne.
Amma matsalar ita ce, tsauraran takunkumi na kara tsananta rashin amincewarmu.
Ri bai ambaci shirin taron koli na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump ba wanda shugaban Amurka ya bayyana a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon wannan makon.
Maimakon haka, ministan ya jaddada tarurruka uku tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata kuma ya kara da cewa: Idan bangaren wannan batun na yaduwar nukiliya ya kasance Koriya ta Kudu ba Amurka ba, yaduwar nukiliya a yankin Koriya ba za ta zo ga irin wannan cikas ba.
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri ya bambanta sosai da na bara, lokacin da ya gaya wa Babban Taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa harin da Amurka ta kai kan Koriya ta Arewa da makamai masu linzami ba zai yiwu ba bayan da Shugaba Trump ya kira Kim "mutumin makamai masu linzami" a kan aikin kashe kansa.
A wannan shekara a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump, wanda a bara ya yi barazanar "hallaka" Koriya ta Arewa, ya yaba wa Kim saboda ƙarfin hali da ya nuna wajen kawar da makaman, amma ya ce akwai sauran aiki da yawa da za a yi kuma dole ne a ci gaba da sanya takunkumi har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da jadawalin wannan, yana cewa "Idan ya dauki shekara biyu, shekara uku ko watanni biyar - ba shi da bambanci".
China da Rasha sun ce Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta amince da matakin da Pyongyang ta dauka.
Duk da haka, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo, a ranar Alhamis, ya gaya wa Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa: Aikace-aikacen takunkumin Kwamitin Tsaro dole ne ya ci gaba da ƙarfi kuma ba tare da tsayawa ba har sai mun cimma cikakken tabbatar da nukiliya.
Kwamitin Tsaro ya kara tsaurara takunkumi kan Koriya ta Arewa tun daga 2006 da nufin dakatar da kudaden da Pyongyang ke baiwa shirin nukiliyarta da na makaman ta.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a gefen babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sannan ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron kolin na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Kudu sau uku a wannan shekarar, amma ziyarar da ya yi ba ta tafi daidai ba.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana mai cewa an samu ci gaba, bayan da Koriya ta Arewa ta soki shi a cikin 'yan sa'o'i kadan saboda yin buƙatun da suka yi kama da na'urori masu laifi.
A wani taron da Moon ya yi a watan jiya, Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin lalata wani sansanin makami mai linzami da kuma makaman nukiliya idan Amurka ta dauki matakan da suka dace.
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa cewa "matakan da suka dace" da yake nema sune tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore da kuma matakai zuwa daidaita dangantakar da Washington.
Daliban Harvard suna koyar da yadda za su samu isashen hutu
Wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard a wannan shekarar ya samu nasarar sa dukkan dalibanta masu digiri na biyu su kara yin bacci domin yaki da al'adar da ke kara bunkasa ta maza da ke nazarin dare-dare da kuma ci gaba da farkawa da maganin kafeyin.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya gano cewa ɗaliban jami'a mafi girma a duniya sau da yawa ba su da masaniya game da ainihin abubuwan da suka shafi kula da kansu.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a likitancin barci a Harvard Medical School kuma kwararre a asibitin Brigham da Women's, ya tsara wannan hanya, wanda ya yi imanin cewa shi ne na farko a Amurka.
An yi wahayi zuwa gare shi don fara karatun bayan ya ba da jawabi game da tasirin rashin barci akan ilmantarwa.
A ƙarshe wata yarinya ta zo wurina ta ce, "Me ya sa kake gaya mini wannan yanzu, da na kai shekara ɗaya?"
Ta ce ba wanda ya taɓa gaya mata muhimmancin barci - abin mamaki,'in ji ta ga The Telegraph.
Wannan darasi, wanda ya fara wannan shekarar, ya bayyana wa dalibai muhimman abubuwa game da yadda al'adun barci mai kyau ke taimakawa wajen samun nasara a makaranta da kuma wasanni, da kuma inganta lafiyarsu.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin tabin hankali a Harvard Medical School kuma babban darektan jami'ar kiwon lafiya, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da karatun ne bayan ta gano cewa daliban suna fama da matsalar rashin bacci a cikin mako.
Wannan darasi na awa daya ya kunshi jerin ayyuka masu ma'amala.
A wani sashe akwai hoton ɗakin kwana inda ɗalibai ke latsa kofi, masu riƙe da kaya, masu motsa jiki da littattafai don su fahimci tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da kuma yadda rashin barci ke shafar wasan motsa jiki, da kuma mahimmancin tsarin barci.
A wani sashe kuma, an gaya wa mahalarta yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya ƙara haɗarin ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, baƙin ciki da kuma ciwon daji.
Bayan haka, taswirar harabar, gumakan hulɗa, suna ƙarfafa mahalarta suyi tunani game da al'adarsu ta yau da kullun.
Mun san cewa ba za ta canja halayen ɗalibai nan da nan ba.
Amma mun yi imanin cewa suna da 'yancin sanin hakan - kamar yadda kai ma kake da 'yancin sanin illolin da shan taba ke haifarwa ga lafiyarka", in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Ya ce, al'adun da ke nuna alfahari da kasancewa a farke duk dare don karatu na wanzu, ya kara da cewa, fasahar zamani da kuma matsin lamba ga dalibai na nufin rashin bacci ya zama matsala mai girma.
Ya ce, tabbatar da samun isasshen barci, mai inganci, ya kamata ya zama makamin sirri na ɗalibai don magance damuwa, gajiya mai tsanani da damuwa - har ma don hana samun nauyi, saboda rashin barci yana sanya kwakwalwa cikin yanayin yunwa, yana sa su jin yunwa koyaushe.
Raymond So, wani dalibi mai shekaru 19 daga California, wanda ke nazarin ilmin sunadarai da ilimin kimiyyar halitta, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler wajen tsara darasin, bayan ya halarci ɗayan azuzuwansa a shekarar da ta gabata a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Ya ce wannan darasin ya buɗe masa idanu kuma ya sa ya nace a kan yin darasi a ko'ina a harabar makarantar.
Mataki na gaba, yana fatan, shine neman dukkan daliban da suka kammala karatun suyi irin wannan shirin karatun kafin su shiga makarantar da ke gasa.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawarar cewa ɗalibai suyi la'akari da yin ƙararrawa don lokacin bacci, da lokacin tashi, kuma su san game da tasirin lalacewar haske mai haske na lantarki da haske na LED, wanda zai iya daidaita tsarin circadian, yana haifar da matsalolin barci.
Livingston 1-0 Rangers: Goal na Menga ya ci wa mutanen Gerrard
Rangers sun sha wahala wani lokaci na baƙin ciki yayin wasa a waje yayin da yajin aikin Dolly Menga ya ba da Steven Gerrard ga kashi 1-0 a Livingston.
Kungiyar Ibrox ta nemi ta samu nasarar cin nasara a wasan da ta yi a St Johnstone, amma Gary Hold ya yi sanadiyyar rashin Gerrard a wasanni 18 da ya yi a matsayin manajan kungiyar, inda ya bar kungiyar ta tazarar maki takwas da manyan 'yan wasan kungiyar, wato Hearts.
