Scott Arfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya jefa kwallon zuwa Scott Robinson, wanda ya kasance mai nutsuwa don zaɓar Menga don kawo ƙarshen aikin.
Gerrard ya amsa a kan birki ta hanyar maye gurbin Coulibaly da Ryan Kent kuma maye gurbin ya ba da kusan tasiri nan take yayin da mai tsaron gida ya yi tsalle a cikin Morelos amma Kelly mai ban sha'awa ya tsere daga layinsa don toshewa.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da jan hankalin baƙi don yin irin wasan da suke so, tare da Lithgow da Halkett suna kama dogon ball bayan dogon ball.
Holt ta iya kara karfinta a gaba a matakai na karshe amma McGregor ya yi tsayin daka don ya ki amincewa da Jacobs kafin Lithgow ta shiga cikin kusurwa.
Mai maye gurbin Rangers Glenn Middleton ya sake neman fanareti a lokacin da yake jayayya da Jacobs amma kuma Thomson ya kalli bangaren.
