HIV/Aids: China ta samu karin sabbin masu cutar kashi 14%
China ta ba da rahoton karuwar kashi 14% na yawan 'yan kasarta da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ne ke fama da cutar a kasar, in ji jami'an lafiya.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai an bayar da rahoton sabbin shari'o'i kusan 40,000.
Yawancin sabbin lamuran sun kasance masu yaduwa ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ke nuna canji daga baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin sakamakon ƙarin jini.
Amma adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin sun fada a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, shekara bayan shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar kanjamau a China ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Yaduwar cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na China.
An haramta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma ana nuna wa LGBT nuna wariya.
Saboda tsattsauran ra'ayin kasar, binciken ya kiyasta cewa kashi 70-90% na maza da ke da jima'i da maza za su auri mata.
Yawancin cututtukan cututtuka sun fito ne daga rashin kariya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan dangantaka.
Tun daga 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samun damar maganin cutar HIV a duk duniya a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa wani ma'aikaci ya bayyana bayanan Sanatocin GOP, ta ce "ƙarya ce mai haɗari" da kuma "ka'idodin rikicewa"
Wakilin Amurka Maxine Waters a ranar Asabar ta yi tir da zargin cewa wani ma'aikacinta ya sanya bayanan sirri na 'yan majalisar dattijai uku na Republican a shafukan Wikipedia na' yan majalisa.
Democrat na Los Angeles ya tabbatar da cewa ana yada jita-jitar ne daga masana da shafukan yanar gizo na dama.
"Karya, karya da karin karya daga masu ikirarin", Waters ta ce a wata sanarwa a shafin Twitter.
Bayanan da aka saki sun hada da adiresoshin gida da lambobin waya na Sanatocin Amurka Lindsey Graham na South Carolina, da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, duka daga Utah.
Bayanai sun bayyana a yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis, wanda wani mutum da ba a san shi ba ya sanya shi a kan Capitol Hill a yayin taron majalisar dattijai game da zargin cin zarafin ɗan majalisa Brett Kavanaugh.
Bayyanawar ta zo ne bayan wasu sanatoci uku sun yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ba da rahoton cewa adireshin IP ɗin da ke gano tushen saƙonnin yana da alaƙa da ofishin Waters kuma ya saki bayanan wani ma'aikacin Waters, Hill ya ruwaito.
Wannan zargin da ba shi da tushe ba karya ne kuma karya ne kwata-kwata, Waters ya ci gaba.
Memba na - wanda aka yi wa barazana da sunansa, bayanansa da kuma tsaronsa sakamakon  wadannan zarge-zarge na karya da na karya - ba shi da wani alhakin bayyana  wannan bayanin.
Wannan da'awar ba ta da tushe kuma ƙarya ce gaba ɗaya.
Bayanin Waters ya jawo martani a kan layi, gami da tsohon sakataren yada labarai na Fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan kin amincewa da ita abin fushi ne", in ji Fleischer.
Wannan ya nuna cewa ba ku da halin zama dan majalisa.
Idan aka zargi mutum da wani abu da bai yi ba, kada ya yi fushi.
Kada ya kasance mai ƙarfi.
Kada ya yi shakkar muradin mai gabatar da kara.
Ya kamata ya kasance mai nutsuwa da kwanciyar hankali.
Fleischer ya bayyana cewa yana kwatanta yadda Waters ya amsa da sukar da 'yan Democrat suka yi wa Alkalin Kotun Kavanaugh, wanda masu sukarsa suka zarge shi da nuna fushi sosai a lokacin zaman ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar Republican da zai tsaya a kujerar Waters a zaben tsakiyar shekara, ya kuma ambaci muryarsa a Twitter.
"Wannan babban abu ne idan gaskiya ne", in ji shi a shafin Twitter.
A cikin sanarwar da ta bayar, Waters ta ce ofishinta ya gargadi hukumomi da hukumomin tilasta yin doka game da waɗannan da'awar na yaudara.
Za mu tabbatar da cewa an gano masu aikata wannan laifin, ya ci gaba, kuma za a riƙe su da alhaki bisa doka saboda duk ayyukan da suka aikata da ke cutarwa da kuma haɗari ga kowane mutum da kuma dukkan ma'aikatan na.
Binciken Johnny English Strikes Again - Rowan Atkinson, kwaikwayon ɗan leƙen asiri mara ƙarfi
Ya zama al'ada yanzu don neman ma'anar Brexit a cikin kowane sabon fim daga mahangar Burtaniya kuma wannan ya zama kamar ya dace da dawowar kamfani na kwaikwayon wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English - wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya sake rayuwa a 2011 tare da Johnny English Reborn.
Shin wani irin wasa da kai game da batun yadda muke da kyau, zai zama damar fitar da sabuwar kasar?
Ko ta yaya, Johnny English mara kyau tare da manyan idanu da ɓangarorin fuskarsa da ba su da kyau sun sake samun lasisi na biyu don yin komai ba daidai ba - wannan sunansa fiye da kowane abu ya nuna cewa shi mai ban dariya ne wanda aka tsara don yankunan masu sauraron fina-finai waɗanda ba su da harshen Turanci.
Tabbas shi ne wawayen jami'an leken asiri wanda duk da irin halayensa na ban mamaki har zuwa kyakkyawa mai kyau yana da kadan daga Clouseau, kadan daga Mr Bean da kuma babban ɓangare na mutumin da ya ba da gudummawar guda ɗaya ga waƙar taken Chariots of Fire a bikin bude gasar Olympics ta 2012 a London.
Hakanan an samo asali ne daga matafiyi da kuma baƙon ɗan ƙasa da ƙasa wanda Atkinson ya taɓa yin nasa bangare a cikin tallan TV na Barclaycard, wanda yanzu an manta da shi, bayan ya bar rikici a baya.
Akwai wani lokacin mai kyau ko biyu a cikin wannan fitowar ta ƙarshe ta JE.
Na ji daɗin lokacin da Johnny English ya zo jirgi mai saukar ungulu da rigar soja ta zamanin dā kuma ya riƙe makamai a kan kwalkwali na ɗan lokaci.
Kyautar Atkinson ga wasan kwaikwayo na jiki ya bayyana, amma abin dariya yana jin daɗi sosai kuma yana da ban mamaki, musamman ma tun lokacin da manyan fina-finai kamar 007 da Mission Impossible kansu suna ba da wasan kwaikwayo a matsayin mai amincewa.
Abin dariya yana jin kamar an yi niyya ne ga yara maimakon manya, kuma a gare ni Johnny English ba shi da ban mamaki da kuma ban mamaki kamar yadda Atkinson ya yi a cikin fim din Bean.
Babban abin da ake magana akai yanzu shi ne cewa Birtaniya na cikin matsala.
Wani dan leken asiri ya kutsa cikin wata babbar hanyar sadarwa ta yanar gizo ta leken asirin Burtaniya, inda ya bayyana sunayen dukkan jami'an Burtaniya a fagen, abin takaici ga jami'in da ke aiki - abin takaici karamin rawa ga Kevin Eldon.
