Masu ba ta shawara kan leken asiri sun sanar da ita cewa duk wani leken asiri da aka yi amfani da shi, zai bukaci ta kwashe wani.
Kuma wannan yana nufin Johnny Ingilishi da kansa, wanda ba shi da ƙwarewa, yanzu yana aiki a matsayin malami a cikin gine-gine masu kyau, amma yana ba da darussan da ba na hukuma ba game da yadda za a zama mai aiki a cikin gida: ɗan wasa mai kyau a nan yayin da Ingilishi ke ba da makarantar leken asiri ta School of Rock.
An dawo da Turanci a Whitehall don tarurruka na gaggawa kuma ya haɗu da tsohon abokin aikinsa mai haƙuri, Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya sake yi.
