Kungiyar Labour ta musanta cewa tana shirin bai wa 'yan Birtaniya damar yin aiki kwanaki hudu a mako amma a biya su kwanaki biyar
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn za ta yi la'akari da wani tsari mai ban mamaki wanda zai ga 'yan Birtaniya suna aiki a mako hudu - amma ana biyan su biyar.
An yi zargin jam'iyyar na son shugabannin kamfanoni su ba ma'aikata sauran abubuwan da suka rage daga juyin juya halin kere kere (AI) ta hanyar ba su wata rana kyauta.
Wannan zai sa ma'aikata su more hutu na kwana uku - amma har yanzu suna samun albashi iri ɗaya.
Majiyoyin sun ce wannan ra'ayi ya saba wa ajandar jam'iyyar da kuma tsare-tsaren tattalin arziki na kasar don karkatar da kasar ga masu aiki.
An amince da sauyawa zuwa mako na kwana hudu a taron ma'aikata a matsayin hanyar da ma'aikata ke amfani da tattalin arzikin da ke canzawa.
Wani babban jami'in jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa jaridar Sunday Times cewa: Ana sa ran sanar da sake duba manufofin kafin karshen shekara.
Wannan ba zai faru ba da dare ba amma mako na  kwana huɗu na aiki shine burin da ya dace da tsarin jam'iyyar don daidaita tattalin arzikin ga ma'aikata da kuma dabarun masana'antar jam'iyyar gaba ɗaya.
Jam'iyyar Labour ba ita ce ta farko da ta amince da irin wannan ra'ayin ba, tare da Jam'iyyar Green Party da ta yi alkawarin mako-mako na kwanaki hudu a lokacin yakin neman zaben shekara ta 2017.
Koyaya, wannan burin a halin yanzu ba shi da amincewa da Jam'iyyar Labour gaba ɗaya.
Wani kakakin jam'iyyar Labour ya ce: "Matsayin aiki na kwana hudu ba siyasa ba ce kuma jam'iyyar ba ta la'akari da hakan".
Shugaban jam'iyyar adawa John McDonnell ya yi amfani da taron 'yan jam'iyyar Labour na makon da ya gabata don bayyana ra'ayinsa na juyin juya halin zamantakewa a tattalin arziki.
Mr McDonnell ya ce ya kuduri aniyar karbe mulki daga hannun 'yan jarida da kuma masu cin gajiyar rashi.
A cewarsa, "a cikin wannan shiri, za a yi amfani da wasu hanyoyin samar da ruwa da kuma samar da ruwa, da kuma samar da ruwa mai amfani da ruwa.
Ya kuma tabbatar da tsare-tsaren sanya ma'aikata a kan allon kamfanoni da ƙirƙirar Asusun mallakar mallaka don ba da kashi 10 cikin ɗari na daidaiton kamfanonin kamfanoni ga ma'aikata, waɗanda ke shirye su karɓi rabon shekara-shekara har zuwa £500.
