Menene Bikin 'Yan Kasa na Duniya da Yin Wani Abu don Rage Talauci?
A ranar Asabar mai zuwa birnin New York zai karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen Festival, wani biki na kiɗa na shekara-shekara wanda ke da jerin fitattun taurari da za su fito da kuma wani babban aiki; don kawo ƙarshen talauci a duniya.
Yanzu, a shekara ta bakwai, bikin na Global Citizen Festival zai ga dubun dubatar mutane sun yi tururuwa zuwa Babban Lawn na Central Park don ba kawai jin daɗin masu fasaha kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, har ma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin manufar taron don kawo ƙarshen talauci ta 2030.
Bikin na Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012, wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya mai wakilci da ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke fafutukar yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta don taron (sai dai idan kuna son biyan tikitin VIP), masu halartar wasan kwaikwayon dole ne su kammala jerin ayyuka, ko ayyuka kamar aikin sa kai, aika imel zuwa shugaban duniya, yin kira ta waya ko wasu hanyoyi masu mahimmanci don taimakawa wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da burin su na kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar da Global Citizen ya samu a cikin shekaru 12 da suka rage don cimma burinsa?
Shin ra'ayin cewa ana ba mutane kyauta kyauta kyauta hanya ce ta gaske don shawo kan mutane su nemi kira zuwa aiki, ko kuma wani misali ne na abin da ake kira "clicktivism" - mutane suna jin suna yin canji na gaske ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takarda kan layi ko aika tweet?
Tun daga 2011, Global Citizen ya ce ya samu sama da ayyuka miliyan 19 daga magoya bayansa, wanda ya shafi dalilai daban-daban.
Ya ce wadannan ayyuka sun taimaka wajen karfafa shugabannin duniya su sanar da alkawura da manufofi da suka kai dala biliyan 37 da ake sa ran za su shafi rayuwar mutane sama da biliyan 2.25 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon 2018, ƙungiyar ta lissafa alkawura 390 kuma ta sanar da ayyukanta, aƙalla dala biliyan 10 daga cikinsu an riga an fitar da su ko an tara su.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudaden da aka samu sun yi tasiri kai tsaye kan mutane kusan miliyan 649 a duniya.
Wasu daga cikin manyan alkawuran sun hada da The Power of Nutrition, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta a Birtaniya ta masu zuba jari da masu aiwatarwa da ke son taimaka wa yara su bunkasa zuwa cikakkiyar damar su, tare da alkawarin samar wa Rwanda da dala miliyan 35 don taimakawa wajen kawo karshen matsalar rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar bayan da suka karbi tweets sama da 4,700 daga 'yan kasa.
Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin kasa, da 'yan kasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya sanya rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a tarihin tarihi, jakadan The Power of Nutrition Tracey Ullman ta fadawa taron a wani taron kai tsaye a Landan a watan Afrilu 2018.
