Jihohi 18 sun goyi bayan kalubalen sabuwar manufar neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan kalubalantar sabuwar manufar Amurka ta hana masu fama da rikicin gida da na kungiyoyi mafaka.
Wakilan jihohi da gundumomi 18 a ranar Juma'a sun shigar da wata kara a gaban kotu a Washington don tallafawa mai neman mafaka da ke kalubalantar manufofin, NBC News ta ruwaito.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai shigar da kara a cikin shari'ar Grace da Sessions da Civil Liberties Union ta gabatar a watan Agusta ba game da manufofin tarayya.
Ta ce abokin aikinta da 'ya'yanta maza 'yan kungiyar ta ta'addanci sun ci zarafinta amma jami'an Amurka sun yi watsi da bukatar da ta yi na neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga watan Yuli.
An tsare ta a Texas.
Lauyoyin jihar da ke goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, waɗanda ke samar da manyan adadin masu neman mafaka a Amurka, yayin da ƙasashen ke fuskantar matsalolin gangs da tashin hankali na cikin gida.
Sabuwar manufar neman mafaka ta Amurka ta soke hukuncin 2014 daga Hukumar Kula da Fitowar Baƙi wanda ya ba da damar baƙi marasa izini da ke tserewa daga tashin hankali na cikin gida don neman mafaka.
A ranar Juma'a, a cikin wata sanarwa, Babban Lauyan Gundumar Columbia Karl Racine, ya ce sabuwar manufar ta yi biris da shekarun da suka gabata na dokar jihar, tarayya da ta duniya.
Dokar tarayya ta bukaci dukkan buƙatun mafaka da a yanke hukunci a kan takamaiman gaskiya da yanayin buƙatar, kuma irin wannan dalili ya karya wannan ƙa'idar, in ji shari'ar abokina.
Lauyoyin sun ci gaba da jayayya cewa idan manufofin hana shiga baƙi suna cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka, suna cewa sun fi dacewa su zama 'yan kasuwa kuma su samar da aikin da ake buƙata.
Babban lauya Jeff Sessions ya umarci alƙalan shige da fice da su daina ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke tserewa daga cin zarafin gida da tashin hankali a watan Yuni.
