Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da yin amfani da tallace-tallace na farfaganda
Mako guda bayan wata jaridar kasar Sin ta buga wata talla a shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke kokarin tallata amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka don yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, a ranar Laraba, ya yi magana game da karin kudin da ake biya na China Daily a cikin Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa - bayan da ya zargi China da neman tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka na 6 ga Nuwamba, zargin da China ta yi masa.
Zargin Trump na cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka shaida wa Reuters cewa sabon mataki ne a wani kamfen da Washington ke yi na matsa lamba kan China.
Yayin da yake al'ada ne ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su yi tallace-tallace don inganta kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a halin yanzu suna cikin yakin cinikayya wanda ke kara tsanantawa wanda ya sa suka ci karo da zagaye na haraji kan shigo da kayayyaki daga kowanne.
A cewar masana'antun, farashin kayayyaki na China ya fi na Amurka yawa.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa mai dogon lokaci, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
China, Branstad ya rubuta a wata sanarwa a jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi, yanzu tana kara wannan cin zarafin ta hanyar tallata farfaganda a cikin 'yan jaridarmu.
A cikin yada farfagandar sa, gwamnatin kasar Sin tana amfani da ƙaunataccen al'adar Amurka ta 'yancin faɗar albarkacin baki da' yan jarida ta hanyar sanya tallan da aka biya a cikin Jaridar Des Moines Register, in ji Branstad.
A akasin haka, a kan jaridar da ke kan titi a nan Beijing, za ka ga muryoyin da ke da iyakacin iko kuma ba za ka ga ainihin ra'ayoyin da jama'ar kasar Sin za su iya yi game da matsalar tattalin arzikin kasar Sin ba, saboda kafofin yada labarai suna karkashin takunkumin jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin, in ji shi.
Ya kara da cewa, wata babbar jarida a kasar Sin ta ki bayar da labarin, ko da yake bai bayyana wacce jarida ba.
'Yan Republican Sun Kashe Mata Masu Zabe A Gaban Zaben Tsakiyar Shekara Da Muhawarar Kavanaugh, Masu Sharhi Sun Yi Gargadi
Yayin da yawancin 'yan Republican ke goyon baya da kare dan majalisar dattijai Brett Kavanaugh a lokacin da yake fuskantar zargin cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za a ga mummunan sakamako, musamman a zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa.
Motsin zuciyarmu game da wannan ya kasance mai girma, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun nuna a hukumance cewa suna so su jagoranci ta hanyar kuri'ar.
Wadannan abubuwa ba za a iya dawo da su ba, "in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin kimiyyar siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell ta Jami'ar Syracuse ga The Hill a wata kasida da aka buga a ranar Asabar.
Reeher ya ce yana shakkar cewa turawa a minti na karshe na Sanata Jeff Flake (R.A.) don binciken FBI zai isa ya kwantar da masu jefa kuri'a.
Mata ba za su manta da itacen jiya ba - ba za su manta da shi gobe ba ko a watan Nuwamba, in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma kakakin kasa na kungiyar masu ci gaba ta MoveOn a ranar Juma'a, a cewar jaridar Washington, D.C.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, masu zanga-zangar sun yi waka "Nuwamba tana zuwa! yayin da suke zanga-zanga a zauren majalisar dattijai yayin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da Kwamitin Shari'a suka yanke shawarar gudanar da nadin Kavanaugh duk da sanarwar da Dr. Christine Blasey Ford ta bayar, Mic ya ruwaito.
Democratic himma da kuma dalili zai zama a  sosai high matakin, ya ce Stu Rothenberg, wani m siyasa Analyst ga labarai site.
Mutane suna cewa sun riga sun yi tsada; kuma gaskiya ne.
Amma za su iya zama mafi girma, musamman tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a da ke jefa kuri'a a unguwannin karkara da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a, masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29, wadanda ba sa son shugaban kasa, amma ba sa yawan kada kuri'a.
Tun kafin sanarwar da Ford ta yi ta bayyana dalla-dalla zargin ta na cin zarafin dan majalisar dattijai, manazarta sun nuna cewa za a iya fuskantar kalubale idan 'yan Republican suka yi nasara.
"Wannan ya zama babban abin takaici ga GOP", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National Committee, a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
Wannan ba wai kawai batun zaben kwamitin ba ne ko kuma na karshe game da ko za a tsige Kavanaugh, amma kuma game da yadda 'yan Republican suka bi da lamarin da kuma yadda suka bi da shi, Guy Cecil, darektan Priorities USA, wata kungiya da ke taimakawa wajen zaben 'yan Democrat, ya shaida wa gidan rediyon.
Duk da haka, Amurkawa suna da alama sun rabu da waɗanda suka gaskata da maganganun Ford da Kavanaugh, tare da ƙarin goyon baya ga na biyun.
Wani sabon bincike da YouGov ya yi ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin ɗari na masu amsa sun gaskata ko kuma sun yi imani da furucin Ford, yayin da kashi 35 cikin ɗari suka ce sun gaskata ko kuma sun yi imani da furucin Ford.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce sun yi tunanin cewa Kavanaugh mai yiwuwa ne ko kuma ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da ya yi wannan bayanin, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari suka ce haka ma game da Ford.
Bayan Flake ya yi watsi da shi, FBI a halin yanzu tana binciken zargin da Ford ya yi da kuma akalla wata mai gabatar da kara, Deborah Ramirez, The Guardian ta ruwaito.
Ford ta shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai a karkashin rantsuwa a makon da ya gabata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata hari a cikin shan giya yana da shekaru 17.
Ramirez ta yi zargin cewa, wanda aka zaba a kotun kolin ya nuna mata gashinsa a lokacin da suke bikin lokacin da suke karatu a Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda Ya Ƙirƙiri Duniyar Yanar Gizo Ya Yi Shirin Ƙirƙirar Sabuwar Intanet Don Yin Gasa da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo mai amfani da intanet, zai kaddamar da wani sabon kamfani da zai yi gasa da Facebook da Amazon da kuma Google.
Sabon aikin almara na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne wanda ke gina kan dandamali mai buɗewa na  Berners-Lee Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma mutanen da suka ba da izinin shiga abin da bayanai.
A wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya bayyana cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce mamayar duniya.
Ya ce, "Ya kamata mu yi shi yanzu", game da sabon kasuwancin.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar kantin sayar da bayanan sirri na kan layi ko POD.
Wannan zai iya ƙunsar jerin sunayen tuntuɓar, jerin abubuwan da za a yi, kalanda, laburaren kiɗa da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Wannan shi ne kamar Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna samuwa a kan daya browser kuma duk a lokaci guda.
Abin da ya sa kantin sayar da bayanan sirri na kan layi na musamman shi ne cewa yana da cikakken amincewa ga mai amfani da shi don samun damar kowane irin bayani.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "kai-da-kai ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar shugaban kamfanin John Bruce, shine kamfanin ya kawo albarkatu, ƙwarewar aiwatarwa da ƙwarewar da ta dace don samar da Solid ga kowa.
Kamfanin a halin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro wanda IBM ya kawo, wasu masu haɓaka ma'aikata waɗanda ke da kwangilar aiki a kan aikin, da ƙungiyar coders masu sa kai.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu haɓaka fasaha a duk faɗin duniya na iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke kan gidan yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa magana da Facebook da Google kan ko su kawo sauyi gaba daya inda duk tsarin kasuwancin su zai koma baya a cikin dare.
Ba ma neman izinin su.
A wani rubutu a kan Medium da aka buga a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa  Manufar  Inrupt ita ce samar da wutar lantarki da tsarin halittu na kasuwanci wanda zai taimaka wajen kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon shafin da aka gina akan Solid. 
A 1994, Berners-Lee ya canza Intanit lokacin da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Ko da lokacin da ya kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance Founder da kuma Daraktan Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya, Gidan yanar gizo da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Open.
"Ina matukar fatan wannan zamani na gaba na yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
