Mickelson wanda bai da lafiya zai ci gaba da zama a kan benci a gasar Ryder Cup a ranar Asabar
Ba'amurke Phil Mickelson zai kafa tarihi a ranar Asabar lokacin da ya buga wasan Ryder Cup karo na 47, amma zai canza salon sa don kauce wa zama babban mataki mara dadi.
Mickelson, wanda ke wasa a cikin taron na shekara-shekara don rikodin 12 sau, ya kasance a kan benci daga kyaftin Jim Furyk don hudu da hudu na Asabar.
Maimakon zama cibiyar aiki, kamar yadda sau da yawa ga Amurka, babban mai nasara sau biyar ya raba ranarsa tsakanin jurewa da aiki akan wasan daga nesa da fatan gyara damuwarsa.
Wanda bai taba buga kwallon daidai ba a lokacin da ya fi tsufa, dan wasan mai shekara 48 ba shi da kyau a filin wasan Le Golf National, inda dogon zango ke sa mutum ya yi kuskure.
Kuma idan hanya kadai ba ta isa ba, Mickelson, a wasa na tara a ranar Lahadi, ya fuskanci zakaran gasar Open ta Burtaniya Francesco Molinari, wanda ya shiga Tommy Fleetwood, sabon shiga kakar wasa, don lashe dukkan wasanninsu hudu a wannan makon.
Idan Amurkawa, da maki hudu a baya a wasan farko na wasanni 12, sun fara da kyau, wasan Mickelson na iya zama babban ci gaba.
Furyk ya nuna amincewarsa ga mijinta, ba zai iya cewa wani abu ba.
"Ya fahimci rawar da ya taka a yau, ya rungume ni a baya ya sanya hannunsa a kaina ya ce zai gama gobe", in ji Furyk.
