An sake jinkirta sabon yakin Jamus
An shirya sabon jirgin ruwan sojin ruwa na Jamus da za a fara aiki a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin jiragen ruwan Cold War da ke aiki, amma ba za a samu ba har zuwa shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma karuwar kudin, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na gida.
An sake dage aikin Rheinland-Pfalz, babban jigon sabon jirgin ruwan Baden-Wuerttemberg, zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019, a cewar jaridar Die Zeit da ke ambaton kakakin soja.
An shirya jirgin don shiga cikin Rundunar Sojojin Ruwa a 2014, amma matsalolin da suka biyo bayan bayarwa sun sabawa makomar wannan babban shiri.
Jiragen ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg da rundunar sojan ruwa ta umarci a 2007 za su maye gurbin jiragen ruwa na Bremen da ke aiki.
An fahimci cewa za su sami babban bindiga, nunin makamai masu linzami da na jirgin sama da kuma wasu fasahohin tsaro, kamar rage radar, masu sanya hannu da infrared da kuma sauti.
Sauran muhimman ayyuka sun haɗa da tsawon lokacin kulawa - wannan ya kamata ya yiwu don aiki da sababbin jiragen ruwa har zuwa shekaru biyu daga tashar jiragen ruwa.
Duk da haka, ci gaba da jinkiri yana nufin cewa sabbin jiragen ruwa - waɗanda ke ba da damar Jamus ta samar da wutar lantarki a cikin teku - za su riga sun tsufa a lokacin da suka shiga sabis, in ji Die Zeit.
Frigirate F125 ta rashin sa'a ta shiga cikin labarai a bara, lokacin da Sojojin Ruwa na Jamus suka ƙi karɓar jirgin kuma suka koma tashar jirgin ruwa ta Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da Sojan Ruwa suka mayar da jirgi zuwa mai gina jirgi bayan an kawo shi.
Ba a san komai game da dalilan ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ambaci wasu   lahani a cikin software da kayan aiki  masu mahimmanci waɗanda suka sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani idan aka tura shi aikin yaƙi.
Rashin software ya kasance mai mahimmanci yayin da jirgin Baden-Wuerttemberg zai kasance da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa 120 - rabin ma'aikata kawai a kan tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Bugu da ƙari, an nuna cewa jirgin yana da nauyin nauyi wanda ya rage aikinsa kuma ya iyakance ikon Naval Fleet don ƙarawa a nan gaba.
Rheinland-Pfalz mai nauyin tan 7,000 an fahimci cewa ya ninka nauyin jirgi na irin wannan ajin da Jamusawa suka yi amfani da shi a Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Baya ga kayan aiki mara kyau, farashin aikin gaba ɗaya - gami da horar da ma'aikatan jirgin - shima yana zama matsala.
An ce wannan ya kai dala biliyan 3.1 ($3.6bn) - daga farkon biliyan 2.2.
Matsalolin sabbin jiragen ruwa sun zama masu mahimmanci musamman a yayin da ake faɗakarwa kwanan nan cewa ƙarfin jirgin ruwan Jamus yana raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus, ya yarda cewa rundunar sojan ruwan yanzu tana da karancin jiragen ruwa da zasu iya jurewa.
Jami'in ya ce matsalar ta kara girma a tsawon lokaci, saboda an tura tsofaffin jiragen ruwa amma ba a samar da wasu ba.
Ya yi korafin cewa babu wani daga cikin frigates na Baden-Wuerttemberg da zai iya shiga cikin Navy.
