Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne girgizar kasa da tsunami mai karfin gaske suka kashe a birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, in ji jami'ai, tare da tsammanin adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Sakamakon lalacewar hanyoyin sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun wani bayani daga yankin Donggala ba, wanda yanki ne a Arewacin Palu wanda ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5.
A birnin Palo, an kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu abubuwa masu muhimmanci game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin  Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin  Tsakiyar Sulawesi ne, wanda ke gefen wani bakin teku a gabar tekun yammacin tsibirin  Sulawesi, tare da yawan mutane kusan 379,800 a 2017.
Sa'ad da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa.
Donggala wani yanki ne da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 mi) na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin  Sulawesi.
A cikin shekarar 2017, yawan mutanen da ke zaune a yankin ya kai kimanin 299,200.
Kifi da noma sune ginshiƙan tattalin arzikin lardin  Central Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Har ila yau, hakar ma'adinai na da muhimmanci a lardin, amma an fi mayar da hankali a Morowali, a bakin tekun Sulawesi.
A cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'o'i ta Indonesia, tsunamis sun afkawa Palu da Donggala sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
A shekarar 1996, tsunami ya kuma afkawa yankin Donggala na yamma, inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana kan Ringin Wuta na Pacific kuma yawan girgizar ƙasa tana faruwa a wurin.
Waɗannan su ne wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da aka yi a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14, wanda ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabi a Aceh.
2005: Ƙarƙashin tekun Sumatra na yamma ya yi fama da wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudu maso gabashin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami mai ƙarfi a gabar kudu, ta kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afku kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta afku a tsibirin Mentawai, a gefen Sumatra, wanda ya haifar da tsunami mai tsayin mita 10 wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 300.
2016: Ƙarƙashin ƙasa ya afku a yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, wanda ya haifar da ɓarna da firgici yayin da mutane ke tunawa da bala'in girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 2004.
Amma, mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu domin wani gini ya rushe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin yawon shakatawa na Lombok a Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a saman tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a cikin keɓewa na ɗan lokaci.
