An kama Palin, mai shekaru 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin cin zarafin mata, da tsoma baki a rahoton cin zarafin mata da kuma tsayayya da kama, a cewar rahoton da 'yan sanda suka fitar a ranar Asabar.
A cewar rahoton 'yan sanda, lokacin da wata mace ta yi kokarin kiran 'yan sanda don bayar da rahoton zargin aikata laifuka, ya kwace mata wayar.
